com.nexmo.client

Class NexmoSeenEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nexmo.client.NexmoEvent
      • com.nexmo.client.NexmoSeenEvent

  • public class NexmoSeenEvent
extends NexmoEvent
    Seen receipt events available for NexmoTextEvent and NexmoAttachmentEvent. A Seen receipt event is explicitly sent with NexmoTextEvent.markAsSeen(NexmoRequestListener) and NexmoAttachmentEvent.markAsSeen(NexmoRequestListener).
